545
00:38:57,630 --> 00:39:02,370
Grandma. But why did everyone gather? Joon Oh's here, too.

546
00:39:02,370 --> 00:39:03,590
Hello, Noona.

547
00:39:03,590 --> 00:39:08,780
We've all been waiting to see you. I heard that you are going to the US next week.

548
00:39:08,780 --> 00:39:09,970
Yes.

549
00:39:09,970 --> 00:39:13,810
That's right. So we gathered to see you

550
00:39:13,810 --> 00:39:18,210
and to have food together. Come and sit!

551
00:39:18,210 --> 00:39:19,360
Yes.

552
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:22,690
Dan Dan, I made your favorite, bulgogi.

553
00:39:22,690 --> 00:39:24,460
It looks good.

554
00:39:24,460 --> 00:39:29,000
Dan Dan, I'm envious. Please invite me when you get all settled.

555
00:39:29,000 --> 00:39:30,710
Hey, me, too!

556
00:39:30,710 --> 00:39:32,720
Me, too, Unni.

557
00:39:35,970 --> 00:39:37,630
Okay, I will.

558
00:39:37,630 --> 00:39:40,210
Let's eat. The soup's getting cold.

